NeoPanel Android ELF

This project is an Android root ELF port and custom panel implementation built with EUI-NEO rendering concepts and primitives.

Upstream EUI-NEO submodule:

https://github.com/sudoevolve/EUI-NEO

The Android ELF Port Kit files under third_party/eui-neo-android-elf-port-kit document and provide Android Surface, Vulkan, and input integration used by this project.
